{{Use dmy dates|date=August 2014}}
{{Use New Zealand English|date=August 2014}}
'''Robert Alexander Wright''' (1853<U+2013>1947) was the [[Mayor of Wellington]] from 1921 to 1925, and a New Zealand politician of the [[New Zealand Reform Party|Reform Party]].

